snippet.textDisplay:
Goosebumps, tears, and so many emotions. What a wonderful journey it’s been. Thank you, thank you and please don’t make us wait another 2 years for the next season. ❤

Ps…great to see Asfar Hussain’s name as one of the writers, please bring him onto the show next season. Also, did I hear Xulfi’s vocals in the background? The set is stunning, breathtaking, as were the CGI effects.  Beautiful voices too.
snippet.textOriginal:
Goosebumps, tears, and so many emotions. What a wonderful journey it’s been. Thank you, thank you and please don’t make us wait another 2 years for the next season. ❤

Ps…great to see Asfar Hussain’s name as one of the writers, please bring him onto the show next season. Also, did I hear Xulfi’s vocals in the background? The set is stunning, breathtaking, as were the CGI effects.  Beautiful voices too.
